  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>A sphere of searing light blossoms into existence to cleanse the universe of the taint of undeath and the metaphysical void. This deals 10d10 vitality damage to all undead creatures in the area with a basic Reflex save. Each living creature in the area restores @Damage[(15 + 5 * @item.level)[healing]] Hit Points. If light scour overlaps with an area of magical darkness or a creature affected by magical darkness, light scour attempts to counteract the darkness effect.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The undead creature is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The undead creature takes half damage.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The undead creature takes full damage.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and @Damage[2d10[persistent,vitality]] damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> Increase the vitality damage to undead by 2d10. Increase the healing to living creatures by 5.</p>"
    },
